### Test Password Reset Flow

### 1. Request Password Reset OTP
POST http://localhost:5454/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rony@student.cuet.ac.bd"
}

### 2. Verify OTP (replace with actual OTP from email)
POST http://localhost:5454/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rony@student.cuet.ac.bd",
  "otp": "123456",
  "type": "password-reset"
}

### 3. Reset Password (use resetToken from step 2)
POST http://localhost:5454/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rony@student.cuet.ac.bd",
  "resetToken": "your-reset-token-here",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123"
}

### 4. Test Login with New Password
POST http://localhost:5454/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rony@student.cuet.ac.bd",
  "password": "NewPassword123"
}

